'''包郵'''又叫'''免费送货'''，是[[實體店|實體店]]或網店（[[淘寶|淘寶]]、[[天貓|天貓]]、[[京東|京東]]等在線店家）銷售商品時聲稱商品可以免費運送至消費者指定的地址，消費者只需支付商品價格，無須額外再支付運費。這其實是一種吸引客户的营销策略，往往商品的快遞費被包含在商品價格中<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2008/07/05/business/yourmoney/05shortcuts.html?ref=business|work=The New York Times|title='Two for One' ... 'Free Delivery' ... Hooked Yet?|first=Alina|author=Tugend|date=5 July 2008|accessdate=2021-02-03|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208080445/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/07/05/business/yourmoney/05shortcuts.html?ref=business|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

